tosdr.case: Tracking via third-party cookies for other purposes without your consent.

title: Tracking via third-party cookies for other purposes without your consent.
quoteText:
Third Party Cookies

Sponsors or advertisers on the WebMD Sites may use their own cookies or other tracking technologies in the banner advertisements and sponsored links and on the pages ("Brand Pages") on the WebMD Sites that consist solely of advertisements or other content from our advertisers.
